org.openstack4j.model.heat

Interface Event

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ModelEntity, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HeatEvent

    public interface Event
extends ModelEntity
    This interface describes the getter-methods (and thus components) of a event. All getters map to the possible return values of Get /v1/​{tenant_id}​/stacks/​{stack_name}​/​{stack_id}​/resources/​{resource_name}​/events/​{event_id}​
    Author:
    Octopus Zhang
    See Also:
    http://developer.openstack.org/api-ref-orchestration-v1.html
